Empower Me
Thoughts by Jonathan Duhon to strengthen your presence and make you stronger. 
These quotes aren't about inspiration but techniques you can use to improve you presence. Many times we set ourselves up to be taken advantage because our behavior invites it. If we change our behavior we can better our interactions.

Empower Me is part of The Me Collection by Jonathan Duhon
